import React from 'react'
import Avatar from '../Avatar'
import { IntroContainer, AboutMe, ResumeLink, Heading } from './IntroElements'

const IntroSection = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <IntroContainer>
                <Avatar />
                <AboutMe>
                    Example text    
                </AboutMe>
                <ResumeLink />
                <Heading>SCROLL OR CLICK THE LINKS AT THE TOP TO SEE MORE :)</Heading>
            </IntroContainer>
        </>
    )
}

export default IntroSection
